	<td class="alt1">
	
		
		
		<!-- message -->
		<div>For roulette, the basic method is doubling bets on the red/black odds. <br />
<br />
starting at 1 an then you double your latest bet on the 1/2 chance each time you loose, by the time you win, you made 1 unit profit.<br />
<br />
But with 0 and 00 green, there is no 1/2 chance. but close enough still.<br />
<br />
you can variate this system by betting on a 1/3 chance and tripling your bet on loosing. this will give you 2 profit on a win but pushes you to the max amount faster.<br />
<br />
playing this method systematically gets you thrown out of the casino, however, the trick is to have a shitload of money and set out multiple gambling lines among several 1/2 and 1/3 pay-off options.<br />
<br />
Since you start betting higher amounts later in the evening, and are getting higher wins also, it gives a more natural image.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
